：有線穩定過、快過無線<br />\n電訊商發射塔都係用光纖互連<br />\n當插住條光纖都做唔到嘅嘢，就算100g都唔會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港美國相矩1.2萬公里，光速一來一回要80ms，呢個延遲係冇乜可能突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e4ead5d9cfc037524d6891c0220a0999419b9f","tid":1241742,"uid":13100,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25267eac39219f03e98cacae2d6e491c0bc3e6b","tid":1241742,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T22:52:17.000Z","msg":"同埋google都話收錢嗰個Stadia Pro係keep住送新game，而且可以stream到4k。<br />\n<br />\n而一般stadia係免費+買game另計錢。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係casual gamer，幾百蚊喺stadia正價買隻game，你就可以喺smart tv／電腦／tablet玩夠佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:11:35.000Z","msg":"新到點先？<br />\n隻game出咗半年先送，咁仲係咪新？<br />\n<br />\n呢種技術只係玩連線game有利，如：鎗game、fifa等，因為本身都係要受延遲<br />\n<br />\n但你地幾個月前玩得咁開心嘅「隻狼」，呢種單機game就無謂玩stadia啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415ce2fb35463c068327c35cfeb19f5f4f281cbc","tid":1241742,"uid":150753,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:19:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8769c45c36fe6ebe84bf0f15301fcbd1e1edba6f","tid":1241742,"uid":13100,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"要做到呢種模式，最少都要各大城市都要起個數據中心，如果要香港連去美國就咪on9啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住就起碼壓到個價去5蚊美金/月<br />\n依家10蚊就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一部ps4壽命6年左右，計佢機價2500蚊hkd+6年psn=1500蚊hkd<br />\n<br />\n4000蚊/72個月=55蚊hkd=6.8美金每個月<br />\n一樣每個月都有舊aaa game送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\