ime":"2019-06-19T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"屋企打online都斷線，<br />\n邊會想玩雲端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"617ebc2c9816af72892cc729c77b8fb1da6bc334","tid":1241742,"uid":104582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"latency 同 throughput 兩樣野wo <br />\n只要throughput 夠，send 個command 既latency  同send 個stream latency 好似係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nisp 都有專用既routing 去滿足低latency 既要求"},{"pid":"93e36a790ab9455acdc8952bac2ab02343d115bb","tid":1241742,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"Google 係全球各地都有data centre 係會連返去最近嘅dc 宜家要連去美國係因為香港未開Stadia<br />\n<br />\n講到台機打LOL 就唔使上網咁 宜家隻隻3A都要連網玩嘅啦 如果要玩到4K 3年俾3千差唔多啦 換機/upgrade都要錢㗎 仲未計你中途壞機要換/維修 PS4 Pro 都3k啦<br />\n<br />\n最後 中國係用唔到google㗎 點打飛機都中冇用"},{"pid":"307990e6ed7479298f08102b0d66aaa6c7e103ee","tid":1241742,"uid":104582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"仲未計edge computing <br />\n主要traffic 同運算去返本地cloud搞, 連線對打既運算先過大平洋（如果真係要連去同美國佬對打）<br />\n<br />\n依家要解決既只係本地cloud 同玩家之間連線夠唔夠throughput ，同某類game latency 要再降低d<br />\n可以話一個5g 解決哂<br />\n<br />\n額外好處仲有打機出cheat 成本大左好多"},{"pid":"fb37f2f376bdc83ce72d8d0b01587f8f6ee46d76","tid":1241742,"uid":13100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93e36a790ab9455acdc8952bac2ab02343d115bb","tid":1241742,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"Google 係全球各地都有data centre 係會連返去最近嘅dc 宜家要連去美國係因為香港未開Stadia<br />\n<br />\n講到台機打LOL 就唔使上網咁 宜家隻隻3A都要連網玩嘅啦 如果要玩到4K 3年俾3千差唔多啦 換機/upgrade都要錢㗎 仲未計你中途壞機要換/維修 PS4 Pro 都3k啦<br />\n<br />\n最後 中國係用唔到google㗎 點打飛機都中冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"原來隻狼唔係3a game<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界唔係得鎗game先係3a 㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal