n再放上server判斷邊個係true state<br />\n而家係連input都有delay, 唔知有咩科技搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解咁多人講5G? 5G快過插LAN線?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"5G只關乎速度嗎?<br />\n<br />\n不!網路的[遲延]，是5G中更重要的一項進步。<br />\n<br />\n目前使用者對智慧型手機下指令(像是開啟一個網路搜尋)與手機實際的運作結果會有時間差，通常會遲延個50到100毫秒，原因在於指令需要通過不同的網路供應者。5G的科技會改善這樣的遲延，到只有1或2毫秒的時間差。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的進步會帶來許多好處，像是虛擬實境，讓使用者更迅速的移動以及使用虛擬實境的設備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似話5g個重點之一係減小delay<br />\n不過暫時好難做到，因為要非常多發射站黎cover"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係話減少去發射站嘅DELAY啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家電話係50MS去發射塔，再80MS去美國<br />\n去到10G都好，降到0.01MS去發射塔都好，都係仲要80MS去美國<br />\n嗰80MS係物理極限，要有時光機先有可能解決啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：我屋企條光纖線已經插住去電訊商度，一定快過你第二十代無線技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e3e61ad6bde5d65ea165d3c53d9c042d5bf25d","tid":1241742,"uid":13100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cda96f892d11a439d7dad77edc08fb224fefd0f8","tid":1241742,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb37f2f376bdc83ce72d8d0b01587f8f6ee46d76","tid":1241742,"uid":13100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93e36a790ab9455acdc8952bac2ab02343d115bb","tid":1241742,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"Google 係全球各地都有data centre 係會連返去最近嘅dc 宜家要連去美國係因為香